TitleEnglish: Star☆Twinkle Pretty Cure: Wish Upon a Celestial Ballad
SummaryEnglish: Star☆Twinkle Pretty Cure: Wish Upon a Celestial Ballad (映画スター☆トゥインクルプリキュア 星の歌に想いをこめて, Star☆Twinkle Pretty Cure: Wish Upon a Celestial Ballad?) is the 27thPretty Cure movie produced by Toei Animation. The movie was released in Japanese cinemas on October 19th, 2019. The Blu-ray and DVD version of the movie was released on February 19th, 2020.
Aliases: Eiga Sutā☆Tuinkuru Purikyua: Hoshi no Uta ni Omoi wo Komete
